- make a project folder
- install node and express
- create subfolders - bin,routes,controllers,models,public,views
- in bin we will have "www" file
- in routes -"index.js" file containing routes
- routes will go to controlles which inturn contains ".js" files
-in views we have ejs/pug templates
-in public we have "css","img","js" subfolders.
